    <body><p><span rend="main_text" rendition="div"><lb />
きその日は<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">思</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">おもひ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>むすぼれ、とぼとぼと<lb />
馬を進むる<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">憂</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">う</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>き旅路、これも旅かや<lb />
まのあたり、<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">路</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">みち</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>のもなかに「愛」の神、<lb />
巡禮姿、しほたれて、<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">衣手</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">ころもて</span><span type="rp">）</span></span><span type="ruby"><span type="rb">輕</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">かろ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>し。<lb />
<lb />
うれはしき<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">其</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">その</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>かんばせは、さながらに、<lb />
<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">位</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">くらゐ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>はがれしやらはれのやつれ姿か、<lb />
<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">憂愁</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">いうしう</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>の<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">思</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">おもひ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>にくれて吐息がち、<lb />
<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">人目</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">ひとめ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>を避けて、うなだるゝあはれの君よ。<lb />
<lb />
ふとしもわれを見給ひて呼び給ふやう、<lb />
『われは、今、かの<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">遠里</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">とほざと</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>をはなれ來ぬ。<lb />
さきにはそこに<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">汝</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">なれ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>が身の<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">心</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">しん</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>の<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">臟</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">ざう</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>をぞ<lb />
<lb />
置きたれど、<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">新</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">あらた</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>の<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">悦</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">よろこび</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>得させむと<lb />
持ち<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">來</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">きた</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>りぬ』とのたまひつ、<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">忽</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">たちま</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>ちわれに<lb />
<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">憑</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">つ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>きたまひ、消え失せたるぞ不思議なる。<lb />
<lb />
<lb />
<lb />
</span></p></body>
